"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-paris-olympics-swimming-slow-pool-stats-science\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"PARIS \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 There is an old saying in thoroughbred racing that could also be applied to Olympic swimming: time only matters when you\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re in jail.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 144, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an old saying\", \"from\": 19, \"to\": 32}, {\"ngram\": \"thoroughbred racing\", \"from\": 36, \"to\": 55}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic swimming\", \"from\": 86, \"to\": 102}, {\"ngram\": \": time\", \"from\": 102, \"to\": 108}, {\"ngram\": \"jail\", \"from\": 139, \"to\": 143}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In other words, you race to win\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094especially at the highest level.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other words\", \"from\": 149, \"to\": 160}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest level\", \"from\": 194, \"to\": 211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How long it takes doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t really matter.\", \"from\": 213, \"to\": 255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And given the number of factors that can affect times, comparing and contrasting them is a tricky task anyway.\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 276}, {\"ngram\": \"factors\", \"from\": 280, \"to\": 287}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 304, \"to\": 309}, {\"ngram\": \"a tricky task\", \"from\": 345, \"to\": 358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the clock rules so many aspects of swimming that it is impossible to disregard.\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the clock\", \"from\": 372, \"to\": 381}, {\"ngram\": \"so many aspects\", \"from\": 388, \"to\": 403}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s been that way since the first time a coach carried a stopwatch.\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 458}, {\"ngram\": \"that way\", \"from\": 464, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 493}, {\"ngram\": \"a coach\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 501}, {\"ngram\": \"a stopwatch\", \"from\": 510, \"to\": 521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World and national rankings are based on times, not how many races someone wins.\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 603, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"World\", \"from\": 523, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"national rankings\", \"from\": 533, \"to\": 550}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 564, \"to\": 569}, {\"ngram\": \"how many races\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 589}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 590, \"to\": 597}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Records are hallowed marks that become etched into the history of the sport.\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 680, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Records\", \"from\": 604, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"hallowed marks\", \"from\": 616, \"to\": 630}, {\"ngram\": \"the history\", \"from\": 655, \"to\": 666}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 679}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now a time-obsessed sport is grappling with the possibility that theParis Olympicsare being contested in a dreaded Slow Pool.\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 807, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a time-obsessed sport\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"the possibility\", \"from\": 726, \"to\": 741}, {\"ngram\": \"theParis Olympicsare\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 767}, {\"ngram\": \"a dreaded Slow Pool\", \"from\": 787, \"to\": 806}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It has become the dominant swimming topic of conversation on the pool deck before and after sessions, in the team areas, in the Olympic Village and on the buses to the venue.\\u00c2 Right or wrong, there has been vigorous vilifying of the La D\\u00c3\\u00a9fense Arena pool\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s depth.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 1075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 936, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4274872059933934e-26, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dominant swimming topic\", \"from\": 822, \"to\": 849}, {\"ngram\": \"conversation\", \"from\": 853, \"to\": 865}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool deck\", \"from\": 869, \"to\": 882}, {\"ngram\": \"sessions\", \"from\": 900, \"to\": 908}, {\"ngram\": \"the team areas\", \"from\": 913, \"to\": 927}, {\"ngram\": \"the buses\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 968}, {\"ngram\": \"the venue\", \"from\": 972, \"to\": 981}, {\"ngram\": \"vigorous vilifying\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1033}, {\"ngram\": \"the La D\\u00c3\\u00a9fense Arena pool\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s depth\", \"from\": 1037, \"to\": 1073}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The temporary pool was built at 2.15 meters, which was deeper than the minimum standard of two meters at the time the Paris Games plans were approved several years ago, but more shallow than current World Aquatics recommendations.\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1306, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The temporary pool\", \"from\": 1076, \"to\": 1094}, {\"ngram\": \"2.15 meters\", \"from\": 1108, \"to\": 1119}, {\"ngram\": \"the minimum standard\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1163}, {\"ngram\": \"two meters\", \"from\": 1167, \"to\": 1177}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1189}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games plans\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"current World Aquatics recommendations\", \"from\": 1267, \"to\": 1305}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those suggest a minimum depth of 2.5 meters, with three meters the ideal measurement.\", \"from\": 1308, \"to\": 1393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a minimum depth\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1337}, {\"ngram\": \"2.5 meters\", \"from\": 1341, \"to\": 1351}, {\"ngram\": \"three meters\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1370}, {\"ngram\": \"the ideal measurement\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The temporary pool in Indianapolis for U.S. Olympic Trials was about 2.8 meters deep.\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1416, \"end\": 1428, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"score\": 0.9967789178085169, \"rank\": 0.003080599727041757, \"text\": \"Indianapolis\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indianapolis\"}, {\"begin\": 1438, \"end\": 1452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"score\": 0.8581582794956577, \"rank\": 0.038961038961052005, \"text\": \"Olympic Trials\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_Olympic_trials_(track_and_field)\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The temporary pool\", \"from\": 1394, \"to\": 1412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many of the high-level meets around the world now are contested at 2.5 or deeper.\", \"from\": 1480, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 1516, \"to\": 1525}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The reason that matters: waves.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1594, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The reason\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1573}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 1588, \"to\": 1593}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The more shallow the pool, the greater the turbulence when swimmers make waves.\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The more shallow the pool\", \"from\": 1595, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"the greater the turbulence\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"swimmers\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1662}, {\"ngram\": \"waves\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The deeper the pool, the calmer the water.\\u00c2 And those who have been observing the closest\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the coaches and competitors\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094say this pool is far from calm.\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1829, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The deeper the pool\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1694}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 1707, \"to\": 1716}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"the closest\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094the coaches\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1778}, {\"ngram\": \"this pool\", \"from\": 1801, \"to\": 1810}, {\"ngram\": \"calm\", \"from\": 1823, \"to\": 1827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s absurdly slow,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says one swimming official who requested anonymity.\", \"from\": 1831, \"to\": 1910, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one swimming official\", \"from\": 1864, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"anonymity\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 1909}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt lacks depth, but it also has strange levels.\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1961, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1916}, {\"ngram\": \"depth\", \"from\": 1923, \"to\": 1928}, {\"ngram\": \"strange levels\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 1960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And when you have a shallow pool with as many underwater cameras as we now have, it doesn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t help settle the water.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d The official said the waves are near-constant in the morning preliminaries, when there are more heats stacked on top of each other.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2214, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a shallow pool\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1994}, {\"ngram\": \"as many underwater cameras\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2026}, {\"ngram\": \"the water.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2081}, {\"ngram\": \"The official\", \"from\": 2082, \"to\": 2094}, {\"ngram\": \"the waves\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2109}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning preliminaries\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2156}, {\"ngram\": \"more heats\", \"from\": 2173, \"to\": 2183}, {\"ngram\": \"top\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2198}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But even at night, the surface is rarely calm.\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2261, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 2227, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2245}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cEven after a seven- or eight-minute break between heats, you can see the water still moving,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d the official says.\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2380, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a seven- or eight-minute break\", \"from\": 2277, \"to\": 2307}, {\"ngram\": \"heats\", \"from\": 2316, \"to\": 2321}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2344}, {\"ngram\": \"the official\", \"from\": 2362, \"to\": 2374}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAnd if you go back and watch videos from other Olympics, you can see the surface of the water is like glass before every final.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Still, there is conflicting evidence regarding the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSlow Pool\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d assertion, and no consensus among coaches and other swimming experts.\", \"from\": 2381, \"to\": 2652, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"videos\", \"from\": 2413, \"to\": 2419}, {\"ngram\": \"other Olympics\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2439}, {\"ngram\": \"the surface\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"the water\", \"from\": 2468, \"to\": 2477}, {\"ngram\": \"glass\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2491}, {\"ngram\": \"every final.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2514}, {\"ngram\": \"conflicting evidence\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2551}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cSlow Pool\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d assertion\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2591}